{
  "type": "page",
  "asideSticky": true,
  "cssVars": {
    "--Page-aside-width": "260px",
    "--Page-body-padding": 0
  },
  "css": {
    ".cxd-AppBcn": {
      "display": "none"
    },
    ".amis-scope .cxd-TableCell-searchPopOver": {
      "min-width": "auto"
    }
  },
  "aside": [
    {
      "type": "page",
      "title": "模型管理",
      "remark": "bla bla bla",
      "toolbar": [
        {
          "type": "button",
          "actionType": "dialog",
          "label": "新增模型",
          "icon": "fa fa-plus pull-left",
          "primary": true,
          "disabledOn": "${models_id}",
          "dialog": {
            "title": "新增模型",
            "body": {
              "type": "form",
              "name": "addModels",
              "api": "/admin/sys/models/addModels",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "input-text",
                  "name": "name",
                  "label": "模型名称",
                  "required": true,
                  "description": "命名格式 模块名_表名 例如:sys_models"
                },
                {
                  "type": "divider"
                },
                {
                  "type": "input-text",
                  "name": "desc",
                  "label": "模型描述",
                  "required": true,
                  "description": "模型说明"
                },
                {
                  "type": "divider"
                },
                {
                  "name": "paranoid",
                  "type": "switch",
                  "label": "偏执表",
                  "value": false,
                  "labelRemark": "paranoid",
                  "description": "Sequelize 支持 paranoid 表的概念. 一个 paranoid 表是一个被告知删除记录时不会真正删除它的表.反而一个名为 deletedAt 的特殊列会将其值设置为该删除请求的时间戳."
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "body": {
        "type": "picker",
        "name": "models_id",
        "joinValues": true,
        "valueField": "id",
        "labelField": "name",
        "label": false,
        "source": {
          "method": "post",
          "url": "/graphql?mdoels=${models}",
          "graphql": "query($orderBy:String, $orderDir:String,$name:String) {item: SysModels_findAll(order: [[$orderBy, $orderDir]],where:{name:{op_substring:$name}}) {id name desc}}",
          "data": {
            "orderBy": "name",
            "orderDir": "${orderDir|default:'asc'}",
            "name": "${name|default:''}"
          }
        },
        "value": "${models_id}",
        "embed": true,
        "pickerSchema": {
          "mode": "table",
          "name": "thelist",
          "autoFillHeight": true,
          "footerToolbar": [
            {
              "type": "tpl",
              "tpl": "当前有 ${COUNT(item)} 个模型。",
              "className": "v-middle pl-3"
            }
          ],
          "headerToolbar": false,
          "columns": [
            {
              "name": "name",
              "label": "模型",
              "sortable": true,
              "searchable": true,
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "operation",
              "label": "",
              "width": 10,
              "className": "text-center",
              "buttons": [
                {
                  "type": "button",
                  "disabledOn": "${models_id}",
                  "icon": "fa fa-times text-danger",
                  "actionType": "ajax",
                  "confirmText": "您确认要删除 $name 吗？删除后可能会导致程序错误！",
                  "tooltip": "删除",
                  "api": {
                    "url": "/graphql",
                    "method": "post",
                    "graphql": "mutation($id:ID!){SysModels_destroy(where:{id:{op_eq:$id}}){count}}",
                    "data": {
                      "id": "${id}"
                    }
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "service",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "tabs",
          "visibleOn": "${models_id>0}",
          "tabsMode": "sidebar",
          "sidePosition": "right",
          "showTip": true,
          "tabs": [
            {
              "title": "基础",
              "icon": "fa-solid fa-table",
              "body": {
                "type": "service",
                "schemaApi": "get:/pages/sys/models/editModels.json?models_id=${models_id}"
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "字段",
              "icon": "fa-solid fa-table-columns",
              "body": {
                "type": "service",
                "schemaApi": "get:/pages/sys/models/fieldModels.json?models_id=${models_id}"
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "索引",
              "icon": "fa-solid fa-trowel-bricks",
              "body": {
                "type": "service",
                "schemaApi": "get:/pages/sys/models/indexesModels.json?models_id=${models_id}"
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "关联",
              "icon": "fa-solid fa-arrows-down-to-people",
              "body": {
                "type": "service",
                "schemaApi": "get:/pages/sys/models/associateModels.json?models_id=${models_id}"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
       
        {
          "type": "wrapper",
          "visibleOn": "${!models_id}",
          "body": {
            "type": "alert",
            "title": "系统提示",
            "body": {
              "type":"tpl",
              "tpl": "<p>请选择左侧的模型进行编辑&nbsp;</p><p>创建模型后会自动生成增、删、改、查的GraphQL接口，<br>具体语法请到<a title=\"GraphQL官网\" href=\"https://graphql.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GraphQL官网</a>查询，具体方法和测试请点击系统顶部【GraphQL】按钮查询。</p>"
            },
            "level": "info",
            "className": "mb-3"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
